19
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:49,060
Okay.

20
00:03:53,860 --> 00:03:54,580
Hello, Shu Yawang.

21
00:03:54,700 --> 00:03:55,300
You...

22
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:56,580
Xia Mu...

23
00:04:16,620 --> 00:04:17,740
It's me! It's me!

24
00:04:17,740 --> 00:04:18,500
It's me.

25
00:04:19,220 --> 00:04:19,860
Yawang,

26
00:04:19,860 --> 00:04:20,540
I'm Xia Mu.

27
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:21,580
Look at me.

28
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:23,060
It's me,

29
00:04:23,340 --> 00:04:23,900
Xia Mu.

30
00:04:28,100 --> 00:04:28,980
Who did this?

31
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:30,340
Tell me.

32
00:04:30,580 --> 00:04:31,340
Who did this?

33
00:04:38,660 --> 00:04:40,860
Do you like the surprise
I prepared for you?

34
00:04:42,980 --> 00:04:43,820
Let go of me.

35
00:04:52,260 --> 00:04:52,860
Do you know?

36
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:56,220
This bracelet that Xiaotian gave you

37
00:04:58,100 --> 00:04:59,540
was from me.

38
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:06,580
I want to go home.

39
00:05:09,460 --> 00:05:10,500
I want to go home.

40
00:05:11,740 --> 00:05:12,820
I want to see Mom.

41
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:17,020
Don't cry.

42
00:05:19,460 --> 00:05:20,540
I'll take you home.

43
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:21,540
Let's go home.

44
00:05:24,260 --> 00:05:24,940
Let's go home.

45
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:30,700
We're going home.

46
00:05:57,100 --> 00:05:57,660
Yawang?

47
00:05:57,820 --> 00:05:58,740
Why are you only home now?

48
00:06:05,700 --> 00:06:06,660
Why are you dressed like this?

49
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:12,860
Yawang!

50
00:06:14,260 --> 00:06:15,220
Who did this?

51
00:06:15,980 --> 00:06:16,820
Tell me.

52
00:06:17,780 --> 00:06:18,860
We'll go to the police.

53
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:30,460
Qu Weiran.

54
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:38,320
[Tang Xiaotian's University
School Grounds]

55
00:06:47,820 --> 00:06:49,180
[Annie, Tang Xiaotian's classmate]
Thinking about your fiancee?

56
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:54,980
Yes.

57
00:06:55,820 --> 00:06:56,820
Surprisingly,

58
00:06:56,820 --> 00:06:57,940
you're quite affectionate.

59
00:07:11,570 --> 00:07:12,500
[Liu Peigang, Qu Weiran's assistant]

60
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:13,060
Mr. Qu,

61
00:07:13,620 --> 00:07:14,700
I've asked the lawyer

62
00:07:14,700 --> 00:07:16,100
to speak to the witnesses last night.

63
00:07:16,100 --> 00:07:17,540
It will be a consensual situation.

64
00:07:19,060 --> 00:07:19,860
Got it.

65
00:07:25,890 --> 00:07:26,870
[Case File]

66
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:43,660
Yawang, don't be afraid.

67
00:07:43,900 --> 00:07:45,020
We've reported it to the police.

68
00:07:45,220 --> 00:07:46,420
The police will handle it.

69
00:07:48,020 --> 00:07:48,780
Yawang.

70
00:07:51,340 --> 00:07:51,780
Xia Mu!

71
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:52,500
What are you trying to do?

72
00:07:52,660 --> 00:07:53,060
Mom!

73
00:07:53,740 --> 00:07:54,140
Stop right there!

74
00:07:56,580 --> 00:07:58,060
See how much I care for you?

75
00:07:59,140 --> 00:08:00,700
Even before being summoned,

76
00:08:00,900 --> 00:08:02,500
I wanted to see you first.

77
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:04,580
You beast!

78
00:08:04,820 --> 00:08:05,940
You'll pay for this!

79
00:08:06,260 --> 00:08:07,020
Mrs. Shu,

80
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:09,140
it was a consensual relationship.

81
00:08:09,820 --> 00:08:12,140
She came to my dinner as my date.

82
00:08:13,180 --> 00:08:15,660
Everyone there saw it.

83
00:08:19,700 --> 00:08:21,180
If you want to play games,

84
00:08:21,780 --> 00:08:24,140
I can do that.

85
00:08:29,740 --> 00:08:30,860
You jerk!

86
00:08:31,380 --> 00:08:32,660
You'll die a nasty death!

87
00:08:47,140 --> 00:08:49,100
It's just been one day
since your fiancee last contacted you.

88
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:50,340
Why are you so anxious?

89
00:09:06,420 --> 00:09:06,780
No.

90
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:08,220
I need to go back.

91
00:09:17,660 --> 00:09:19,100
[Criminal Evidence Law]
The camera footage has been deleted.

92
00:09:20,140 --> 00:09:21,900
Any trace of evidence
has been wiped clean.

93
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:24,860
All the witness statements
are not in our favor either.

94
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:26,420
Now,

95
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:29,180
it's very hard to prove
Qu Weiran is guilty.

96
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:00,990
♪Thinking that having nothing means♪

97
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:04,990
♪I can be fearless♪

98
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:09,390
♪Like a knight putting on a cloak♪

99
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:15,430
♪Charging toward unknown danger♪

100
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:24,750
♪That promise deeply buried
like the wind♪

101
00:10:25,540 --> 00:10:26,380
It's my fault.

102
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:28,470
If I had answered your call...

103
00:10:30,740 --> 00:10:31,660
It's not your fault.

104
00:10:31,660 --> 00:10:32,950
♪Let those memories run freely♪

105
00:10:33,860 --> 00:10:34,540
I'm sorry.

106
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:37,070
♪Through the cracks♪

107
00:10:39,380 --> 00:10:40,500
Go back and have a good sleep.

108
00:10:41,060 --> 00:10:41,940
I'm fine.

109
00:10:41,940 --> 00:10:45,510
♪And they still hurt♪

110
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,910
♪As long as my hands
are pressed together♪

111
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:49,950
♪Whether it's sincere or not♪

112
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:53,340
♪With solitary bravery♪

113
00:10:53,340 --> 00:10:55,140
I'll always be by your side.

114
00:10:57,420 --> 00:10:58,060
Okay.

115
00:10:58,060 --> 00:11:01,750
♪Enduring the cold winter♪

116
00:11:05,700 --> 00:11:06,340
Ya.

117
00:11:19,820 --> 00:11:21,460
♪SO RE MI♪

118
00:11:22,980 --> 00:11:26,940
♪I can't help thinking♪

119
00:11:27,940 --> 00:11:31,220
♪A happy or sad ending♪

120
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:35,980
♪Is up to us♪

121
00:11:36,420 --> 00:11:40,180
♪Lovers are always forced to part♪

122
00:11:41,180 --> 00:11:44,100
♪How dramatic♪

123
00:11:45,380 --> 00:11:48,660
♪Doing my best to run to you♪

124
00:11:49,300 --> 00:11:54,340
♪And our happy ending♪

125
00:11:54,820 --> 00:11:57,140
♪If I can meet you again♪

126
00:11:57,460 --> 00:11:59,420
♪And write this story again♪

127
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:03,380
♪I don't believe in fate♪

128
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:06,780
♪If I can hug you again♪

129
00:12:07,220 --> 00:12:08,540
♪I don't care♪

130
00:12:08,540 --> 00:12:11,860
♪About the bitter past♪

131
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:14,620
♪Let all our partings♪

132
00:12:14,620 --> 00:12:16,700
♪Indifference and struggles♪

133
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:19,980
♪Return to when we met♪

134
00:12:20,620 --> 00:12:23,620
♪As the crowd disappears♪

135
00:12:24,060 --> 00:12:25,380
♪It's still you♪

136
00:12:25,380 --> 00:12:31,740
♪Watching the sunset with me♪

137
00:12:32,780 --> 00:12:35,340
♪If we start again♪

138
